{
  "stem": "4700.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when you came late, the people who were there for a while, they got the bits along the wall, where they could perhaps put a nail into the wall.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when you came late, you were in the middle where everybody walked over you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had to go to the loo at nighttime, because everybody had dysentery.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So of course, we were in the middle of the room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember like today, it was near the steps to the shop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the boards were worn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were extremely uneven.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were like a washboard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I could never find a spot to lie to, because just to lie on the-- on the floorboards was highly uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I've done it many times as a scout, but it was difficult.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a friend came and said to us, we should find some protected occupation and told us what would be advisable.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother got a job as a nursing sister for old people because nobody wanted to do it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The old people all suffered from dysentery, and lice, and God knows what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there were no sanitary means at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, the toilets were highly inadequate and everything was highly inadequate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to get people do that, they decided to make it a protected occupation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother did that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because I did this graphic course, I got a job in the-- the Germans had a-- in the [GERMAN], they devoted [BACKGROUND NOISE] the upper floor to have people who were artists, painters, and so forth, to draw pictures.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they printed them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they colored them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to color them in with aniline paints.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they sold those pictures as bookmarks or calendars and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
